text: IRM 2.13.11 is to be used by User and Network Services, IRS contractors, and IRS organizations and personnel that perform or support any telecommunication and networking information technology security activities. As of June 30, 2016 Information in IRM 2.13.11 is obsoleted and will go into the Service Catalog as catalog items, and the other content will be divided into User Guides, Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs), Knowledge Articles, and posted as information on SharePoint sites.
